Package edu.vanier.selfdriving.controllers

Class GameControllerAI

java.lang.Object
edu.vanier.selfdriving.controllers.GameController
edu.vanier.selfdriving.controllers.GameControllerAI
public class GameControllerAI extends GameController
GameController child class that is used for AI controlled game mode to control the network visualizer and network of the cars.
